      "content": "i mean \"practical reality\" sounds like you're saying the free trade side is just a fantasy or something. if most experts say tariffs cause deadweight loss and hurt the poor most, isn't it kinda biased to call them \"necessary\" instead of just saying it's one way of looking at it?",
